President Obama congratulates Prime Minister Narendra Modi and the new Indian government on their swearing-in. The President emphasizes the deep bond and commitment between India and the United States, as the world's two largest democracies. They share a common goal of promoting economic opportunity, freedom, and security for their people and the world. The statement expresses the desire to work closely together with the new government to strengthen and expand the U.S.-India strategic partnership in the future.